fulltitle: Steve Coleman - Cardiovascular - Rhythmic Voice Leading - Habana, Cuba
description:
Sitting on the Malecón in Habana, Cuba - discussing the shifting relationship of the rhythm to the clave in my composition 'Cardiovascular' (from the recording 'Functional Arrhythmias').

You can hear this song here:
http://m-base.org/functional_arrhythmias_mp3_files/Cardiovascular.mp3

You can purchase the  'Functional Arrhythmias' CD here:
http://pirecordings.com/album/pi47
